    com.kontakt.sdk.core.interfaces.changelog.MapChangelog<UUID,com.kontakt.sdk.core.interfaces.model.IAction<Device>>
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class ActionMapChangelog
extends com.kontakt.sdk.core.data.changelog.AbstractMapChangelog<UUID,com.kontakt.sdk.core.interfaces.model.IAction<Device>>
    Map Changelogs act as maps where the keys are requested characteristic properties of elements and values are Changelogs consisting of added, modified and deleted elements. In order to obtain Map Changelog you must request by with REST client (KontaktApiClient) Action Map Changelog contains Action Changelogs for specified beacon Ids. The beacon Ids are the backed map keys whereas the Changelogs are the values. Changelogs in Android SDK v1.0.6 are deprecated and will be removed in the next versions.
